  "instructions": [
    "Soak 12 bamboo skewers in water for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread chicken pieces onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until chicken is cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, prepare peanut sauce by blending peanuts, coconut milk, fish sauce, brown sugar, lime juice, and chili peppers in a blender until smooth.",
    "Heat 25ml of vegetable oil in a pan over medium heat. Add sliced shallots and fry until crispy, about 5 minutes. Drain on paper towels.",
    "To serve, place a few grilled skewers on a plate, spoon some peanut sauce on top, and garnish with fresh basil leaves and crispy fried shallots.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Optional: serve with steamed rice or noodles for a more filling meal."
  ],
